/**
 * Minimal database email query service (T036h)
 *
 * Read-only queries for email testing - no complex filtering or performance optimization.
 * Defers comprehensive query capabilities to full T048 implementation.
 *
 * Core Functions:
 * - fetchEmailsByDateRange: Fetch emails within date range for batch testing
 * - fetchEmailById: Fetch single email for isolated testing
 * - fetchUnclassifiedEmails: Fetch emails without classification_session records
